text: KGIL is a class A radio station broadcasting a country music format to Johannesburg, California. ==History== KGIL began broadcasting on April 11, 2011. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Mass media in Kern County, California Category:Country radio stations in the United States GIL (FM) Category:Radio stations established in 2013 Category:2013 establishments in California
